#: panel-plugin/buttons/wckbuttons-dialogs.glade:180
msgid ""
"Put the buttons id in the desired order.\n"
"Example: [HMC]\n"
"H=Hide, M=Maximize/unMaximize, C=Close"
msgstr ""
"ວາງໄອດີປຸ່ມຕາມລໍາດັບທີ່ຕ້ອງການ.\n"
"ຕົວຢ່າງ: [HMC]\n"
"H=ເຊື່ອງ, M=ຂະຫຍາຍ/ຄືນຄ່າ, C=ປິດ"

#: panel-plugin/buttons/wckbuttons-dialogs.glade:209
#: panel-plugin/menu/wckmenu-dialogs.glade:141
#: panel-plugin/title/wcktitle-dialogs.glade:441
