msgid "Put the maximized window buttons on the panel."
msgstr "ວາງປຸ່ມໜ້າຕ່າງທີ່ຂະຫຍາຍໃຫຍ່ສຸດໄວ້ໃນພາເນລ."

#: panel-plugin/menu/wckmenu-dialogs.glade:61
#: panel-plugin/title/wcktitle-dialogs.glade:95
